         full_name = park_name)

  visitation_data %>%

tent_campers_plot <- plot_ly(visit_summary, 
                             x = ~as.factor(month), 
                             y = ~total_tent, 
                             type = "scatter", 
                             mode = "lines", 
                             color = ~park_type,
                             legendgroup = ~park_type) %>%
  layout(title = "Tent Campers")

backcountry_plot <- plot_ly(visit_summary, 
                            x = ~as.factor(month), 
                            y = ~backcountry_visits, 
                            type = "scatter",
                            mode = "lines",
                            color = ~park_type,
                           legendgroup = ~park_type,
                           showlegend = FALSE) %>%
  layout(title = "Backcountry")

rv_campers_plot <- plot_ly(visit_summary, 
                           x = ~as.factor(month), 
                           y = ~total_rv, 
                           type = "scatter", 
                           mode = "lines",
                           color = ~park_type,
                          legendgroup = ~park_type,
                          showlegend = FALSE) %>%
  layout(title = "RV Campers")

subplot(
